  <span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Ambox_content.png" class="mw-file-description"><img src="/images/f/f4/Ambox_content.png" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="40" height="40" class="mw-file-element"></a></span></div></td>
